  "title": "Market Risk Analyst",
  "description": "<p>Our client, an MNC within the Fortune 500 involved in the Oil & Gas industry, is presently looking for a <strong>Market Risk Analyst</strong> to join their growing team.</p><p>As part of a 13-man team, the <strong>Market Risk Analyst</strong> will take ownership of market risk management activities, including daily monitoring, reporting, and in-depth analysis of risk exposures across the company’s trading and commercial portfolios. Reporting to the Head of Risk, the incumbent role include assessing market movements and volatility, identifying key price drivers, validating trader inputs/positions, and ensuring the accuracy of P/L and exposure data.</p><p>Successful candidates can expect to work in a fast-paced work environment with a great cohesive team for the established organization.<br /></p><p><strong>REQUIREMENTS:</strong></p><ul><li>Possess at least a Degree in Finance, Business Management, Economics or equivalent</li><li>At least 3 years of working experience in market risk within Energy/Oil & Gas trading house</li><li>Working experience IN Oil, Gas, Energy, Chemical products would be an advantage</li><li>Strong proficiency in MS Office (including MS Excel) and Power BI</li></ul><p>Interested applicants kindly use the apply button or send in your application in MS word format to <a href=\"mailto:XXXX@onyxrecruit.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Kelvin.</a>Tan at/onyxrecuit.com.sg(R22111268| EA: 18C9213)</p><p><em>*We regret that due to potential volume of responses, not all applicants be contacted.</em></p>",
